<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Six college units may be awarded for Advanced Placement Examination scores of 3 or higher, depending upon the test, and exemptions can be made to general education courses. Maximum number of units earned via AP Exam is 30.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.menlo.edu/admissions/ap-ib-and-level-credit" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
